<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٤٢ - حَدَّثَنَا<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٤١⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span> <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3">آدَمُ </a>قَالَ: حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2779">شُعْبَةُ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3479">عَبْدِ الْعَزِيزِ بْنِ صُهَيْبٍ </a>قَالَ: سَمِعْتُ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/822">أَنَسًا </a>يَقُولُ: <span class="c2">«كَانَ النَّبِيُّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> إِذَا دَخَلَ الْخَلَاءَ قَالَ: اللَّهُمَّ إِنِّي أَعُوذُ بِكَ مِنَ الْخُبُثِ وَالْخَبَائِثِ»</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>تَابَعَهُ ابْنُ عَرْعَرَةَ عَنْ شُعْبَةَ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>وَقَالَ غُنْدَرٌ،<span class="c5"> عَنْ شُعْبَةَ:</span> إِذَا أَتَى الْخَلَاءَ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>وَقَالَ مُوسَى،<span class="c5"> عَنْ حَمَّادٍ:</span> إِذَا دَخَلَ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ سَعِيدُ بْنُ زَيْدٍ:</span> حَدَّثَنَا عَبْدُ الْعَزِيزِ: إِذَا أَرَادَ أَنْ يَدْخُلَ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>